column5: Is there anywhere to shoot sporting clays near Lac Suel?
Right next to the bike trails....sorry could not resist.
Garry, you're my kind of fisherman. Many times, on trips down to southern IL lakes, we take the shotguns along, and spend a morning at the range at Rend lake state park. HRG
...and I don't care who you are.
Off the top of the houseboat. Be sure to use bio-clays and steel shot. LOL..
